not chronologically , but rather more thought @-@ tanks for thought , the Munich @-@ born on June 1 , 1947 wrote his memoirs , each chapter initiated by a suitable lyrics text .
and he is ruthlessly honest : from Onanie as a Gymnasiast to shoplifting and drug use , he does not cause human weakness .
also to show how he himself learned tolerance in dealing with his fellow human beings .
