this informed a court speaker on Monday .
it is stated in the plea that Achenbach had cheated in buying works of art and vintage timers and Berthold Albrecht calculated higher than actually paid purchase prices .
as a result , the agreed commission would have been higher .
Achenbach bought valuables for Albrecht for € 121 million .
