I know of families where new children were born , but also of widows who have never married again .
it is difficult to accept that life will continue , even if we do not want it .
I will never forget how my heart sprang in me when I saw him in hospital .
and now I see what is happening in the world - wars in other regions .
what are these people fighting for ?
why are they killing each other ?
war is now very close to our country and I almost cannot believe that .
we used to be a friendly country , how can it be that we are fighting now ?
people and children are suffering , I am sure that many children have been killed and many are still killed in Ukraine .
if we could only attack and throw out all these rebels - as far as possible .
